<br />

<br />
A seafury cyclops begins to chant.
<br />
Your song ends.
<br />
You slow down.
<br />
Your feet move faster.
<br />
You slow down.
<br />
A seafury cyclops hits YOU for 76 points of damage.
<br />
You are stunned!
<br />

<br />
Well i found out that this issue is a conspiration!
<br />

<br />
When you kite and that happens, you put yourself in a very dangerous situation. If the train manages to catch you before you get to restart selo's, you die.
<br />

<br />
When you die, you loose exeperience.
<br />

<br />
If you can't find a cleric, you have to make up for the lost of experience.
<br />

<br />
And as we all know, experience in Everquest, is time.
<br />

<br />
The more time you pass playing the game = more money for SoE.
<br />

<br />
A + B + C = ABC
<br />

<br />
Selo's bug is a conspiration.
<br />

<br />
Erydan Ouragan</span></td>
