			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>The reason for it only dropping from the caster is that there's a data transmission delay on the part of the server to get the casting of your song off to the rest of your group.  If the timing was &quot;perfect&quot; enough to cause the buff disappearance bug on your side, then the subsecond delay getting the effect data to everyone else usually causes it to be &quot;imperpect&quot; enough to land on them.</span></td>
